{"tid":861066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"料八成工種未來20年內消失 曾俊華促改革教育制度","createTime":"2018-10-13T19:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T01:42:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b9086bc239b293337365356f2e2e39d5208ff46","tid":861066,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_7JOyIAfFbrKRPC2A1Mf5g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20181013a125249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_7JOyIAfFbrKRPC2A1Mf5g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20181013a125249.jpg&h=ab74af34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】前財政司司長曾俊華指科技發展已超乎學校教育能力，但本港的教育制度卻仍沿用工業時代的藍圖，認為有需要改革。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華今日出席論壇致辭時，講述他對21世紀教育的看法。他預期隨著科技發展，七至八成現有工種未來20年或會逐漸消失，而學生難以像以往般，在人生的中頭20年學畢足以應付一生需要的知識。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華批評現今的教育方法不合時宜，令學生得不到適當的工具、知識甚至思維去應付未來遇到的新問題，削弱競爭力。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華建議更理性分配智識，在不同成長階段適時吸收，教育制度也要改革，學生需要學習全新知識、技術、工作模式，甚至價值觀。"},{"pid":"b010130b9a9c629f0ab99c581a42a934c8f60764","tid":861066,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T00:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e762f4a8ef2af54264beedb925adcd5347aa7e9","tid":861066,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T00:13:55.000Z","msg":"係8成人類消失, 因為有skynet"},{"pid":"40827272fbc6aec9fa73db27b06e20ba61639c48","tid":861066,"uid":42764,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T00:29:20.000Z","msg":"香港科技教育就係搵班唔識stem既教師教學生stem<br />\n搵班唔識高中中文既教師教中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb2b792d3cf30beb8ba3111d66147c9814dd626","tid":861066,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T00:30:32.000Z","msg":"晨早就要<img src=\"/assets/